OL,3,CCrypto firms to be regulated like
OL,4,Cother assets under new UK rules
OL,6,FCryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin will
OL,7,Fbe regulated in a similar way to other
OL,8,Ffinance products under new UK laws
OL,9,Fcoming into force in 2027.
OL,11,FThe Treasury announced legislation
OL,12,Fwhich will mean crypto firms have to
OL,13,Fmeet a set of standards and rules
OL,14,Foverseen by the Financial Conduct
OL,15,FAuthority (FCA).
OL,17,FIt follows efforts to overhaul the
OL,18,Fmarket which has grown in popularity
OL,19,Fin recent years as an alternative
OL,20,Finvestment product and a way of making
OL,21,Fpayments.
