OL,3,CCrypto firms to be regulated like
OL,4,Cother assets under new UK rules
OL,6,FBut it has not been subject to the
OL,7,Fsame regulation as traditional finance
OL,8,Fproducts such as stocks and shares,
OL,9,Fwhich means consumers may not get the
OL,10,Fsame level of protection.
OL,12,FThe Government said the new rules,
OL,13,Fcoming into force in 2027, will make
OL,14,Fthe industry more transparent and make
OL,15,Fit easier to detect suspicious
OL,16,Factivity, impose sanctions or hold
OL,17,Ffirms to account over their activity.
