OL,3,CCrypto firms to be regulated like
OL,4,Cother assets under new UK rules
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said:
OL,7,F"Bringing crypto into the regulatory
OL,8,Fperimeter is a crucial step in
OL,9,Fsecuring the UK's position as a world-
OL,10,Fleading financial centre in the
OL,11,Fdigital age.
OL,13,F"By giving firms clear rules of the
OL,14,Froad, we are providing the certainty
OL,15,Fthey need to invest, innovate and
OL,16,Fcreate high-skilled jobs here in the
OL,17,FUK, while giving millions strong
OL,18,Fconsumer protections, and locking
OL,19,Fdodgy actors out of the UK market."
