OL,3,CCrypto firms to be regulated like
OL,4,Cother assets under new UK rules
OL,6,FCrypto firms, which can include crypto
OL,7,Fexchanges and digital wallets,
OL,8,Fcurrently have to register with the
OL,9,FFCA if they provide services that fall
OL,10,Fwithin the scope of money laundering
OL,11,Fregulations.
OL,13,FThe changes will bring firms that
OL,14,Fprovide crypto services into the remit
OL,15,Fof the FCA with the intention of
OL,16,Fsupporting legitimate businesses.
